WEBVTT

00:01.187 --> 00:03.612
Hey, Charles, can we talk in
the briefing room for a sec?

00:03.648 --> 00:05.412
- There's a question I gotta ask you.
- Mm-hmm.

00:08.243 --> 00:10.219
It's happening.

00:10.255 --> 00:11.750
Jake is gonna pop the question.

00:11.786 --> 00:13.885
- He's gonna ask me to be his BM.
- Both: No.

00:13.921 --> 00:15.816
BM, best man, is a common abbreviation.

00:15.849 --> 00:17.785
No one but you has ever used it.

00:17.818 --> 00:19.322
I am so relieved.

00:19.358 --> 00:21.394
I thought maybe he was gonna
ask one of Amy's brothers

00:21.430 --> 00:22.698
or, ugh, Sarge.

00:22.734 --> 00:24.525
- Hey, man, come on.
- Charles!

00:24.558 --> 00:27.061
[mouthing]

00:27.981 --> 00:31.199
Okay, so I know this is a lot to ask...

00:31.232 --> 00:32.500
No, it's not. I want to do it.

00:32.533 --> 00:34.086
You want to cover my shift this weekend

00:34.122 --> 00:35.472
so I can go to the White Plains Mall

00:35.508 --> 00:37.550
and meet Darryl Strawberry at the
opening of a cellphone store?

00:38.315 --> 00:39.407
Yes.

00:39.674 --> 00:41.474
It's exactly what I was hoping
you'd ask.

00:41.510 --> 00:43.644
Great. Thanks. You sure it's okay?

00:43.677 --> 00:45.446
Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

00:45.479 --> 00:47.776
I'm very happy about it.
It'll be fun. It'll be fun.

00:47.812 --> 00:50.165
Uh, look at my smile. Have to go now.

00:51.619 --> 00:53.321
All: Surprise!

00:53.354 --> 00:55.289
Oh, my God!

00:55.323 --> 00:57.137
- Jake!
- What do you say, bud?

00:57.173 --> 01:00.738
- Will you be my BM?
- Yes! Yes, a million times, yes!

01:01.082 --> 01:02.569
In your face, Terry!

01:02.605 --> 01:04.119
What? I'm holding a sparkler for you.

01:04.155 --> 01:05.633
I helped organize a lot of this.

01:05.666 --> 01:07.413
Well, you can stick that
sparkler up your butt.

01:07.449 --> 01:08.950
I'm the best man!

01:08.986 --> 01:11.839
[upbeat music]

